===Places to eat===
  â
Interesting places to eat in Sarikei include the two coffeeshops in the Nyelong Industrial Estate, which serve Kam Pua noodles as well as [http://www.alexallied.com/reviews/sarikeis-asam-tom-yam-prawn-noodle Prawn Noodles]. Aik Seng coffeeshop serves Roti Kahwin, Laksa, Nasi Lemak and a version of Kam Pua noodles.
  â   â
A KFC and a local fast food franchise called Sugar Bun serve the local populace.
  â   â
Taman Selera at Kampung Seberang is one of the hottest spot at night serving different types of halal food ranging from Satay to local version Z@aikin Pizza.
